name: Ironhack's Instagram Clone
description:
Ironhack Workshop #1 - Overview & Frames

In this file, you will find the skeleton of Instagram's 2020 interface. Use the features in Figma to populate and complete the designs. You can place your own photographs!

The focus of this workshop is that you have a comprehensive overview of how to work with Figma and that you nail the concept of Frames. 

As a result of the workshop, you'll have created an infinite scroll interface ^^
